#: src/qalc.cc:2494 src/qalc.cc:6229
msgid "Algebraic Mode"
msgstr "代數模式"

#: src/qalc.cc:2496
msgid "Determines if the expression is factorized or not after calculation."
msgstr "決定是否在計算後將表達式分解為因子。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2497
msgid "Determines if unknown values will be assumed non-zero (x/x=1)."
msgstr "決定是否將未知值假設為非零(x/x=1)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2498
msgid "Display a message after a value has been assumed non-zero."
msgstr "值假設非零後顯示一個訊息。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2502
msgid "Default assumptions for unknown variables."
msgstr "未知變數的預設假設。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2531 src/qalc.cc:6267
msgid "Calculation"
msgstr "計算"

#: src/qalc.cc:2533
msgid "Default angle unit for trigonometric functions."
msgstr "三角函數的預設角度單位。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2537
msgid ""
"How approximate variables and calculations are handled. In exact mode "
"approximate values will not be calculated."
msgstr "如何處置近似變數和計算。在精確模式中不會計算近似值。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2538
msgid ""
"If activated, interval arithmetic determines the final precision of "
"calculations (avoids wrong results after loss of significance) with "
"approximate functions and/or irrational numbers."
msgstr ""
"如果啟用，則區間算術決定具有近似函數和/或無理數計算的最終精確度(在失去有效值"
"後避免錯誤的結果)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2539
msgid ""
"Determines the method used for interval calculation / uncertainty "
"propagation."
msgstr "決定用於區間計算/誤差傳播的方法。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2542
msgid ""
"Specifies the default number of significant digits displayed and determines "
"the precision used for approximate calculations."
msgstr "指定顯示有效數字的預設數量和決定用於近似計算的精確度。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2547 src/qalc.cc:6304
msgid "Enabled Objects"
msgstr "啟用物件"

#: src/qalc.cc:2555
msgid "Interpret undefined symbols in expressions as unknown variables."
msgstr "將表達式中的未定義符號解釋為未知變數。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2557
msgid ""
"If activated physical constants include units (e.g. c = 299 792 458 m∕s)."
msgstr "如果啟用，則物理常數包含單位(例如c = 299 792 458 m∕s)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2559 src/qalc.cc:6316
msgid "Generic Display Options"
msgstr "通用顯示選項"

#: src/qalc.cc:2561
msgid "Use abbreviated names for units and variables."
msgstr "單位和變數使用縮寫名稱。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2562
msgid "Use colors to highlight different elements of expressions and results."
msgstr "使用顏色凸顯表達式和結果的不同元素。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2565
msgid "Always place negative values last."
msgstr "總是將負值放最後。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2568
msgid "Add extra space around operators."
msgstr "在運算子周圍增加額外的空白。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2570
msgid "Display Unicode characters."
msgstr "顯示Unicode字元。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2571
msgid "Display exponents 0-9 using Unicode superscript characters."
msgstr "使用Unicode上標字元顯示指數0-9。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2572
msgid "Add empty lines before and after result."
msgstr "結果前後加入空白列。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2574 src/qalc.cc:6353
msgid "Numerical Display"
msgstr "數值顯示"

#: src/qalc.cc:2577 src/qalc.cc:2741
msgid "bin"
msgstr "bin"

#: src/qalc.cc:2579 src/qalc.cc:2743
msgid "oct"
msgstr "oct"

#: src/qalc.cc:2581 src/qalc.cc:2745
msgid "dec"
msgstr "dec"

#: src/qalc.cc:2583 src/qalc.cc:2747
msgid "hex"
msgstr "hex"

#: src/qalc.cc:2585
msgid "sexa"
msgstr "sexa"

#: src/qalc.cc:2617 src/qalc.cc:2717
msgid "Determines the default decimal separator."
msgstr "決定預設的小數分隔符。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2634
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of displayed significant digits (by default determined "
"by precision)."
msgstr "指定顯示有效數字的數量(預設由精確度決定)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2643
msgid ""
"Determines how scientific notation are displayed (e.g. 3E6, 3e6, or 3 * "
"10^6)."
msgstr "決定如何顯示科學記法(例如3E6、3e6、或3 * 10^6)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2654
msgid ""
"Determines how rational numbers are displayed (e.g. 5/4 = 1 + 1/4 = 1.25). "
"'long' removes limits on the size of the numerator and denominator."
msgstr ""
"決定如何顯示有理數(例如5/4 = 1 + 1/4 = 1.25)。\"長\"移除分子和分母大小的限"
"制。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2655
msgid ""
"Enables two's complement representation for display of negative hexadecimal "
"numbers."
msgstr "啟用二的補數表示法顯示負十六進制數字。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2656 src/qalc.cc:2738
msgid "Use 'j' (instead of 'i') as default symbol for the imaginary unit."
msgstr "使用'j'(而不是'i')作為虛數單位的預設符號。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2658
msgid "Use lowercase letters for number bases > 10."
msgstr "底數>10使用小寫字母。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2679
msgid ""
"If activated, 1/6 is displayed as '0.1 666...', otherwise as '0.166667'."
msgstr "如果啟用，則1/6顯示為\"0.1 666...\"，否則為\"0.166667\"。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2683
msgid "Determines how approximate numbers are rounded."
msgstr "決定如何捨入近似數字。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2686
msgid "Determines how scientific notation is used (e.g. 5 543 000 = 5.543E6)."
msgstr "決定如何使用科學記法(例如5 543 000 = 5.543E6)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2707
msgid "If activated, zeroes are kept at the end of approximate numbers."
msgstr "如果啟用，則保持零在近似數字的結尾。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2708
msgid ""
"Enables two's complement representation for display of negative binary "
"numbers."
msgstr "啟用二的補數表示法顯示負二進制數字。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2709
msgid "Use special symbols for digits 10 and 11 in numbers with base 12."
msgstr "在底數12的數字中對數字10和11使用特殊的符號。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2711 src/qalc.cc:6542
msgid "Parsing"
msgstr "剖析"

#: src/qalc.cc:2713
msgid "Use ^ as bitwise exclusive OR operator."
msgstr "使用^作為按位元互斥或運算子。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2714
msgid "Allow input of uncertainty using concise notation."
msgstr "允許使用簡潔記法輸入誤差。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2731
msgid ""
"Enables two's complement representation for input of negative hexadecimal "
"numbers. All hexadecimal numbers starting with 8 or higher are negative, "
"unless binary bits is set."
msgstr ""
"啟用二的補數表示法輸入負十六進制數字。所有以8或更高起始的十六進制數字都是負"
"數，除非設定二進制位元。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2733
msgid "Allows use of ',' as thousands separator."
msgstr "允許使用','作為千位分隔符。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2736
msgid "Allows use of '.' as thousands separator."
msgstr "允許使用'.'作為千位分隔符。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2764
msgid "See 'help parsing mode'."
msgstr "請觀看\"help parsing mode\"。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2765
msgid ""
"If activated, numbers are interpreted as approximations with precision equal "
"to the number of significant digits (3.20 = 3.20+/-0.005)."
msgstr ""
"如果啟用，則數字解釋為精確度等於有效位數的近似值(3.20 = 3.20+/-0.005)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2766
msgid ""
"Interpret addition/subtraction of percentage as percentage increase/decrease "
"of the first term (100 + 10% = 110)."
msgstr "將百分比的加法/減法解釋為第一項增加/減少的百分比(100 + 10% = 110)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2767
msgid ""
"Enables two's complement representation for input of negative binary "
"numbers. All binary numbers starting with 1 are negative, unless binary bits "
"is set."
msgstr ""
"啟用二的補數表示法輸入負二進制數字。所有以1起始的二進制數字都是負數，除非設定"
"二進制位元。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2769 src/qalc.cc:6594
msgid "Units"
msgstr "單位"

#: src/qalc.cc:2771
msgid "Enables automatic use of hecto, deca, deci, and centi."
msgstr "啟用自動使用百、十、分和厘。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2774
msgid ""
"Controls automatic unit conversion of the result. 'optimalsi' always "
"converts non-SI units, while 'optimal' only converts to unit expressions "
"with less units and exponents."
msgstr ""
"控制結果的自動單位轉換。\"最佳SI\"總是轉換非SI單位，而\"最佳\"只轉換到具有較"
"少單位和指數的單位表達式。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2794
msgid ""
"If activated, binary prefixes are used by default for information units."
msgstr "如果啟用，則資訊單位預設使用二進制前綴。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2795
msgid ""
"Enables automatic conversion to the local currency when optimal unit "
"conversion is enabled."
msgstr "啟用最佳單位轉換時，能夠自動轉換到本地貨幣。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2805
msgid ""
"Enables automatic use of prefixes in the denominator of unit expressions."
msgstr "啟用在單位表達式的分母中自動使用前綴。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2806
msgid ""
"If activated, units are separated from variables at the end of the result."
msgstr "如果啟用，則在結果結尾將單位從變數分離。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2807
msgid "Enables automatic use of prefixes in the result."
msgstr "啟用在結果中自動使用前綴。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2808
msgid ""
"Use negative exponents instead of division for units in result (m/s = "
"m*s^-1)."
msgstr "在結果中單位使用負指數而不是除法(m/s = m*s^-1)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:2810
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Determines how expressions with temperature units are calculated (hybrid "
"acts as absolute if the expression contains different temperature units, "
"otherwise as relative)."
msgstr ""
"決定如何計算具有溫度單位的表達式(如果表達式包含不同的溫度單位，則混合充當絕"
"對，否則充當相對)。"

