msgid "Commands for RPN mode:"
msgstr "RPN模式的命令:"

#: src/qalc.cc:6716
msgid "STATE"
msgstr "狀態"

#: src/qalc.cc:6719 src/qalc.cc:6721
msgid "INDEX"
msgstr "索引"

#: src/qalc.cc:6720 src/qalc.cc:6723
msgid "INDEX 1"
msgstr "索引1"

#: src/qalc.cc:6720 src/qalc.cc:6723
msgid "INDEX 2"
msgstr "索引2"

#: src/qalc.cc:6722
msgid "DIRECTION"
msgstr "方向"

#: src/qalc.cc:6725
msgid "Type help COMMAND for more information (example: help save)."
msgstr "鍵入\"help 命令\"以獲取更多資訊(範例: help save)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6726
msgid ""
"Type info NAME for information about a function, variable, unit, or prefix "
"(example: info sin)."
msgstr ""
"鍵入\"info 名稱\"以獲取有關函數、變數、單位或前綴的資訊(範例: info sin)。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6727
msgid ""
"When a line begins with '/', the following text is always interpreted as a "
"command."
msgstr "當行以'/'開頭時，之後的文字總是解釋為命令。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6753 src/qalc.cc:6759
msgid "currencies"
msgstr "貨幣"

#: src/qalc.cc:6773
msgid "No function, variable, unit, or prefix with specified name exist."
msgstr "沒有具有指定名稱的函數、變數、單位或前綴存在。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6781
msgid "Factorizes the current result."
msgstr "分解目前結果。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6785
msgid "Applies partial fraction decomposition to the current result."
msgstr "將部分分式分解套用到目前結果。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6789
msgid "Expands the current result."
msgstr "展開目前結果。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6795
msgid "Set default assumptions for unknown variables."
msgstr "設定未知變數的預設假設。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6824
msgid ""
"Saves the current result in a variable with the specified name. You may "
"optionally also provide a category (default \"Temporary\") and a title."
msgstr ""
"將目前結果儲存在指定名稱的變數中。你還可以選擇提供類別(預設\"臨時\")和標題。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6825
msgid ""
"If name equals \"mode\" or \"definitions\", the current mode and "
"definitions, respectively, will be saved."
msgstr "如果名稱等於\"模式\"或\"定義\"，則分別儲存目前的模式和定義。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6827
msgid "Example: store var1."
msgstr "範例: store var1。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6831
msgid "Clears the screen."
msgstr "清除螢幕。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6836
msgid "Lists the expression history."
msgstr "列出表達式歷史記錄。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6840
msgid "Clears the expression history."
msgstr "清除表達式歷史記錄。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6845
msgid "Create a variable with the specified name and expression."
msgstr "建立一個具有指定名稱和表達式的變數。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6847
msgid "Example: variable var1 pi / 2."
msgstr "範例: variable var1 pi / 2。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6851
msgid "Creates a function with the specified name and expression."
msgstr "建立一個具有指定名稱和表達式的函數。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6852
msgid "Use '\\x', '\\y', '\\z', '\\a', etc. for arguments in the expression."
msgstr "在表達式中使用'\\x'、'\\y'、'\\z'、'\\a'等等作為引數。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6854
msgid "Example: function func1 5*\\x."
msgstr "範例: function func1 5*\\x。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6858
msgid "Removes the user-defined variable or function with the specified name."
msgstr "移除指定名稱的使用者定義的變數或函數。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6860
msgid "Example: delete var1."
msgstr "範例: delete var1。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6864
msgid ""
"Make the temporary user-defined variable or function with the specified name "
"non-temporary."
msgstr "使指定名稱的使用者定義的臨時變數或函數非臨時。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6866
msgid "Example: keep var1."
msgstr "範例: keep var1。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6870
msgid "Displays the current mode."
msgstr "顯示目前模式。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6874
msgid "Displays a list of variables, functions, units, and prefixes."
msgstr "顯示變數、函數、單位和前綴的列表。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6875
msgid ""
"Enter with argument 'currencies', 'functions', 'variables', 'units', or "
"'prefixes' to show a list of all currencies, functions, variables, units, or "
"prefixes. Enter a search term to find matching variables, functions, units, "
"and/or prefixes. If command is called with no argument all user-defined "
"objects are listed."
msgstr ""
"輸入引數\"貨幣\"、\"函數\"、\"變數\"、\"單位\"或\"前綴\"，以顯示所有貨幣、函"
"數、變數、單位或前綴的列表。輸入搜尋項以尋找匹配的變數、函數、單位和/或前綴。"
"如果沒有用引數呼叫命令，則列出所有使用者定義的物件。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6877
msgid "Example: list functions."
msgstr "範例: list functions。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6878
msgid "Example: find dinar."
msgstr "範例: find dinar。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6879
msgid "Example: find variables planck."
msgstr "範例: find variables planck。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6883
msgid "Displays information about a function, variable, unit, or prefix."
msgstr "顯示有關函數、變數、單位或前綴的資訊。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6885
msgid "Example: info sin."
msgstr "範例: info sin。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6889
msgid "Downloads current exchange rates from the Internet."
msgstr "從網際網路下載目前匯率。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6893
msgid "(De)activates the Reverse Polish Notation stack and syntax."
msgstr "(停)啟用逆波蘭記法堆疊和語法。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6895
msgid ""
"\"syntax\" activates only the RPN syntax and \"stack\" enables the RPN stack."
msgstr "\"語法\"只啟用RPN語法，而\"堆叠\"啟用RPN堆叠。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6896
msgid "\"on\" (1) and \"off\" (0) (de)activates both."
msgstr "\"on\"(1)和\"off\"(0)(停)啟用兩者。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6900
msgid "Clears the entire RPN stack."
msgstr "清除整個RPN堆疊。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6904
msgid "Removes the top of the RPN stack or the value at the specified index."
msgstr "移除RPN堆疊的頂部或在指定索引的值。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6906 src/qalc.cc:6918 src/qalc.cc:6928 src/qalc.cc:6938
msgid ""
"Index 1 is the top of stack and negative index values count from the bottom "
"of the stack."
msgstr "索引1是堆疊的頂部，而負索引值從堆疊的底部計數。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6910
msgid "Displays the RPN stack."
msgstr "顯示RPN堆疊。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6914
msgid "Swaps position of values on the RPN stack."
msgstr "在RPN堆疊上交換值的位置。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6916
msgid ""
"If no index is specified, the values on the top of the stack (index 1 and "
"index 2) will be swapped and if only one index is specified, the value at "
"this index will be swapped with the top value."
msgstr ""
"如果未指定索引，則交換堆疊頂部的值(索引1和索引2)，而如果只指定一個索引，則在"
"此索引的值將與頂部值交換。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6920
msgid "Example: swap 2 4"
msgstr "範例: swap 2 4"

#: src/qalc.cc:6924
msgid "Duplicates a value on the RPN stack to the top of the stack."
msgstr "將RPN堆疊上的值複製到堆疊的頂部。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6926
msgid "If no index is specified, the top of the stack is duplicated."
msgstr "如果未指定索引，則複製堆疊的頂部。"

#: src/qalc.cc:6932
msgid "Rotates the RPN stack up (default) or down."
msgstr "將RPN堆疊向上(預設)或向下旋轉。"

