#: libqalculate/BuiltinFunctions-util.cc:1343
msgid ""
"Plots one or more expressions or vectors. Use a vector for the first "
"argument to plot multiple series. Only the first argument is used for vector "
"series. It is also possible to plot a matrix where each row is a pair of x "
"and y values."
msgstr ""
"繪製一個或多個表達式或向量。第一個引數使用向量來繪製多個序列。向量序列只使用"
"第一個引數。也可以繪製一個矩陣，其中每一列是一對x和y值。"

#: libqalculate/BuiltinFunctions-util.cc:1345
msgid ""
"Additional arguments specify various plot options. Enter the name of the "
"option and the desired value, either separated by space or as separate "
"arguments. For most options, the value can be omitted to enable a default "
"active value. For options with named values, the option name can be omitted "
"(otherwise the value can be replaced by an integer, representing the index "
"of the value starting from zero). If the first option specified is a "
"numerical value, this is interpreted as either sampling rate (for integers > "
"10) or step value."
msgstr ""
"其他引數指定各種繪圖選項。輸入選項的名稱和期望的值，用空白分離或作為個別的引"
"數。對於大多數選項，可以省略該值以啟用預設的作用值。對於具有命名值的選項，可"
"以省略選項名稱(否則可以用整數替換該值，表示該值的索引從零開始)。如果指定的第"
"一個選項是數字值，則將此解釋為採樣率(對於整數>10)或步長值。"

